# Design & Vibe Rules — UPDATED (Much Lighter & Brighter)

Overall theme must feel extremely light, airy, bright and sunlit.
- Very high lightness / brightness level (even lighter than current Figma)
- Warm, welcoming Nigerian hospitality feel — premium but fresh and open
- Never dark or heavy

Exact Color Palette (use these exact hex codes):
- Background / Main surface: #FEFAF4 (very light warm cream, almost white)
- Secondary surface / Cards: #FFFDF9
- Primary Accent (buttons, CTAs, highlights): #E88A5F (bright, warm terracotta-orange)
- Secondary Accent / Trust color:rgb(80, 0, 133) (bright, fresh forest green)
- Text Primary: #1F2A24 (deep but not black)
- Text Secondary: #3F4A44
- Borders / Subtle dividers: #F0EDE6

Real Estate hero must feel bright, cinematic and premium (like rangedevelopmentsgroup.com but even lighter and more open).

All components, dashboards, property cards, navigation, etc. must use this brighter palette consistently.